Class GlobeViewState

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mousebird.maply.ViewState
      • com.mousebird.maply.GlobeViewState

  • public class GlobeViewState
extends ViewState
    The map view state encapsulates what's in a view at a certain point in time. It's here so we can pass that around without fear of making a mess.

    In general, toolkit users shouldn't need to interact with these.
